# Configuration
## Guild Name: {{guild_name}}
- {{emoji_guild}} | Guild level for the coalition: **{{guild_lvl}}**
- {{emoji_khan}} | To configure channels and the role for khan
- When you have finished configuring the bot, press the **Publish** button to post your registration announcement. If you want to delete your registration announcement, press the **Delete** button.
- This bot is designed to help players register for khan. It manages khan registrations and displays them in a dedicated channel.
This bot is in no way affiliated with the coalition and its administrators. If you have any questions or suggestions, please contact the bot developers on this [server](https://discord.gg/bxTpCJFdnF).

This menu allows you to configure the bot.
